text: Natalia Cordova-Buckley (born November 25, 1982) is a Mexican actress. She was born in Mexico City. Cordova-Buckley is best known for playing Elena "Yo-Yo" Rodriguez on Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. and as the voice of Frida Kahlo in Disney-Pixar Coco (2017). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican movie actors Category:Mexican television actors Category:Mexican voice actors Category:Actors from Mexico City
